*Thursday night was fucking the best ever! If I could repeat it a million and one times, I WOULD! I couldnt have asked for it to be more perfect. For starters..Everyone was telling me that my outfit looked much better than they thought. Second..I was so glad that I asked Kathryn to it because we had so much fun together. I loved being around her and of course I thought the kiss was perfect. Details..ha, First we are sitting at one of the tables and I reminded her that we still needed to "question mark in the question mark" (dice) and then later we were slow dancing and I went in for a "warmer-upper" lol, and she said she was glad that I had asked her earlier..so later I specifically remember her saying that she liked the song, and all i kept thinking was "damn we should kiss now so that it is even better." Another reason it was so good is because we didn't have to end the night when the dance ended. (9:00PM ugh) A bunch of us went to the Cheesecake Factory for dessert there was: Andrea, Diana, KT, Monica, Holli, Emily, Karen, and of course Kat and I. Anyway, her mom and dad drove Holli and I back and on the way we cuddled and she half way slept on me and once we got there she came to the door and I gave her flowers and she was so suprised. Everything was perfect!

Prom was last night!! ANYWAYS THE DRAMA HA HA!!! ok here goes, matt and i have this, just pure cold hate for each other, he kept trying to mosh so that he could punch me and get away with it...heres the funny part...he never got to hit me so he made up a story that he punched me in the face and now every1 is like "oh i heard u got ur ass kicked last nite" and im like "no nothing happen" so on monday matt is gonna look dumb cuz every1 i was hangin out with knows that nothing happen!!!!! BUT THE GOOD PART FLASHINGS and TOUNGE!!!!!!!!!!! hellz yea biznatch!
